OL,4,C'must urgently improve customer
OL,5,Cservice'
OL,7,FScottish Power, Ovo Energy and British
OL,8,FGas must "urgently" improve their
OL,9,Fcustomer service after a survey found
OL,10,Fthey are the worst energy suppliers
OL,11,Ffor responding quickly and effectively
OL,12,Fto problems, Which? said.
OL,14,FThe watchdog said "all too often"
OL,15,Fconsumers were being left on hold,
OL,16,Fstuck in never-ending chatbot loops or
OL,17,Fpassed from department to department
OL,18,Fwith no resolution or helpful answer
OL,19,Fto their query.
