OL,7,FScottish Power came bottom, receiving
OL,8,Fa satisfaction score of minus 13 out
OL,9,Fof a possible 100 for how long it took
OL,10,Fto get in touch with a person who
OL,11,Fcould help, and a score of three for
OL,12,Fhow long it took to get an answer to
OL,13,Fan issue or query.
OL,15,FOne customer said that after being
OL,16,Fleft on hold when trying to phone his
OL,17,Fsupplier about a billing issue, and
OL,18,Fthen speaking to an agent who was
OL,19,Funable to help, he suffered sleepless
OL,20,Fnights and anxiety over the unresolved
OL,21,Fproblem.
